{"tid":1888730,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"提防網軍萬能金句:「咁得閒__,唔見你屌下___ 」","createTime":"2020-02-20T11:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T23:51:25.000Z","uid":69221,"like":44,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6a05490673c9c4048037caf3c5e531de5d9de74e","tid":1888730,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔係新鮮野<br />\n就係屈你冇做另一樣更重要嘅事，而叫停正在討論嘅議題<br />\n<br />\n泛民賣港？唔屌得<br />\n「咁得閒屌泛民,唔見你屌下建制 」<br />\n左膠害死人？唔屌得<br />\n「咁得閒屌自己人，唔見你屌下黑警 」<br />\n要私了藍絲？唔好令自己變成野獸！<br />\n「咁得閒打普通人，唔見你打下黑警 」<br />\n最近嘅就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「咁得閒屌Youtuber ，唔見你屌下藍絲 」</span><br />\n先睇下柒頭一號點幫李萬機兜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a03qLQ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa03qLQ1.png&h=ca5bb789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六號之所以收皮，係因為佢歪曲事實之後我地嘅即時大反擊，呢度要多謝tvb戰線嘅各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同理銘仔都係，佢柒完之後被廣傳，subscribe 狂跌一半，即時收左皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反映到群眾監察嘅力量<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府之所以咁放肆就係因為現行制度下民意冇影響力</span></em><br />\n但演藝界唔係，自媒體時代民意就係錢，失民心就係過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n仲有柒頭二號唔俾人話黃店難食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLcOJCG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLcOJCG.png&h=4a1a5ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面已有完美反駁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2Xi50c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2Xi50c.png&h=657dd787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有公眾做錯野講錯野，就要討論，辯明是非，用群眾力量去令佢承擔後果，有誤會就提出，想補救就道歉/表明立場，絕對唔係抹殺言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有獨栽社會先會禁止言論"},{"pid":"78d2cf0d15c9f1ead5cf096975990c8e093a7cee","tid":1888730,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17587f4f88a2043f6a